# Machine Learning & Data
# =========================
# Ignore datasets to save space
*.csv
*.xlsx
*.json
*.sqlite
*.db

# NOTE: We are intentionally NOT ignoring *.pkl here
# because Render needs your mental_health_pipeline.pkl file to run the FastAPI app!

